UPDATE 12.01.2012:
more items, fixxed deathrun, fixxed vents, new rooms, new weapons, ... ''ba_jail_zombie_future_v2''

ba\_jail\_zombie\_future\_2011 you liked? ba\_jail\_zombie_future\_2011 is continuing and is now available for download. If you think now that has not changed much where you're wrong. There are new secret passages, new textures, new rooms, new weapons and items are and much more. Some mistakes were corrected the map.
The Chamber will now heal faster healing, it is now possible to kill the zombie, the brightness of the map was increased. etc. Please download the map and make yourself a picture!
Please write a comment how you find the card or to add me in steam. : D
